            <h2>Donation & Support Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-container">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        How are donations used?
                        <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Donations directly support our team's activities including:</p>
                        <ul class="faq-list">
                            <li>Registration fees for regional and national competitions</li>
                            <li>Robot parts and building materials</li>
                            <li>Tools and equipment</li>
                            <li>Team travel expenses</li>
                            <li>Team uniforms and promotional materials</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Continue with your existing FAQ items -->
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        Can I donate equipment instead of money?
                        <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Absolutely! We welcome in-kind donations of tools, materials, and equipment. Please contact us to discuss specific needs and arrange for delivery or pickup of donated items, or use our equipment donation form above.</p>
                    </div>
